1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:57,620 --> 00:02:00,120
[Love Under The Full Moon]

3
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:03,120
[Episode 5]

4
00:02:13,790 --> 00:02:14,540
[Xiao Dong.]

5
00:02:15,190 --> 00:02:16,270
Is that girl with you?

6
00:02:17,390 --> 00:02:18,750
Yes, she is with me.

7
00:02:19,510 --> 00:02:20,350
By the way, Prof. Chen,

8
00:02:20,750 --> 00:02:21,579
she has a name now.

9
00:02:22,070 --> 00:02:23,030
Her name is Lei Chu Xia.

10
00:02:23,590 --> 00:02:24,470
Lei Chu Xia?

11
00:02:24,470 --> 00:02:25,910
This name is quite romantic.

12
00:02:25,950 --> 00:02:28,150
Sure, let me talk to Lei Chu Xia.

13
00:02:28,350 --> 00:02:28,910
I have a good news.

14
00:02:29,470 --> 00:02:29,829
Okay.

15
00:02:32,510 --> 00:02:33,310
Prof. Chen is on the line.

16
00:02:34,750 --> 00:02:35,710
Prof. Chen?

17
00:02:38,790 --> 00:02:39,510
Prof. Chen.

18
00:02:39,790 --> 00:02:40,620
Lei Chu Xia.

19
00:02:40,870 --> 00:02:41,790
Congratulations.

20
00:02:41,790 --> 00:02:42,630
[Finally you have a name.]

21
00:02:42,910 --> 00:02:43,510
[It's like this.]

22
00:02:43,790 --> 00:02:45,190
My lab

23
00:02:45,190 --> 00:02:46,390
has received a donation.

24
00:02:46,630 --> 00:02:47,590
Now, I have enough fund

25
00:02:47,590 --> 00:02:48,870
to conduct the research

26
00:02:48,870 --> 00:02:50,350
on the device that can control your energy.

27
00:02:51,180 --> 00:02:51,750
Does that mean...

28
00:02:52,430 --> 00:02:53,630
Does that mean

29
00:02:54,110 --> 00:02:55,550
I may be able to move around freely in the future?

30
00:02:55,990 --> 00:02:56,550
I can also

31
00:02:56,550 --> 00:02:57,510
go back to my parents?

32
00:02:57,670 --> 00:02:58,790
Technically, it can work that way.

33
00:02:58,910 --> 00:03:00,190
However, you will have to wait

34
00:03:00,190 --> 00:03:01,230
[I succeed in the research.]

35
00:03:01,430 --> 00:03:02,310
Thank you.

36
00:03:03,630 --> 00:03:04,430
Did you hear that?

37
00:03:04,710 --> 00:03:05,350
I may be able to go back

38
00:03:05,350 --> 00:03:06,110
to my parents.

39
00:03:06,110 --> 00:03:06,750
Yes.

40
00:03:12,110 --> 00:03:12,829
[Chu Xia.]

41
00:03:13,790 --> 00:03:14,790
[When I see your smile,]

42
00:03:15,380 --> 00:03:16,390
[everything is worth it.]

43
00:03:20,640 --> 00:03:21,960
[Six hours ago]

44
00:03:21,960 --> 00:03:23,870
[Donation, ten million yuan]

45
00:03:23,870 --> 00:03:26,070
Sponsoring our lab?

46
00:03:29,710 --> 00:03:30,550
Yes, Prof. Chen.

47
00:03:31,790 --> 00:03:32,710
Why?

48
00:03:33,420 --> 00:03:34,350
Actually I

49
00:03:35,110 --> 00:03:36,390
have been obsessed about science since I was young.

50
00:03:36,710 --> 00:03:37,430
Therefore, I hope

51
00:03:37,430 --> 00:03:38,950
the science research in our homeland

52
00:03:39,350 --> 00:03:40,510
can thrive with each passing day.

53
00:03:40,829 --> 00:03:41,829
Please accept

54
00:03:42,110 --> 00:03:43,190
the donation, Prof. Chen.

55
00:03:44,150 --> 00:03:44,990
Why?

56
00:03:45,790 --> 00:03:47,430
There are so many labs out there.

57
00:03:47,670 --> 00:03:49,030
Why do you sponsor only us?

58
00:03:49,510 --> 00:03:50,790
It's like this, Prof. Chen.

59
00:03:51,710 --> 00:03:52,780
There is another reason.

60
00:03:53,510 --> 00:03:54,470
My friend,

61
00:03:54,750 --> 00:03:55,790
Winter, also known as the God of Gaming,

62
00:03:56,110 --> 00:03:57,270
is currently working on

63
00:03:57,430 --> 00:03:58,670
a universe related game.

64
00:03:58,910 --> 00:04:00,270
I don't play game.

65
00:04:00,270 --> 00:04:01,990
Everyone in the university knows that

66
00:04:02,190 --> 00:04:03,110
I have useless hands.

67
00:04:03,510 --> 00:04:04,510
Actually, we hope that

68
00:04:04,510 --> 00:04:05,350
you can

69
00:04:05,550 --> 00:04:06,190
help the Winter team out

70
00:04:06,190 --> 00:04:07,589
by consulting us on the universe

71
00:04:07,790 --> 00:04:09,510
from time to time

72
00:04:09,709 --> 00:04:11,510
when we are developing the game.

73
00:04:15,430 --> 00:04:16,630
Now it makes sense.

74
00:04:16,910 --> 00:04:18,110
It's consultation after all.

75
00:04:19,710 --> 00:04:21,030
[It's so hard to spend the money.]

76
00:04:21,430 --> 00:04:22,190
[How irritating.]

77
00:04:22,870 --> 00:04:23,830
Okay, everything is all right.

78
00:04:24,190 --> 00:04:24,790
Okay?

79
00:04:25,390 --> 00:04:26,340
Thank you so much.

80
00:04:26,750 --> 00:04:28,590
Prof. Chen, I have to go.

81
00:04:28,830 --> 00:04:29,710
All right, let me send you off.

82
00:04:30,430 --> 00:04:31,470
If you ever need help,

83
00:04:31,590 --> 00:04:32,350
you can get my consultation anytime.

84
00:04:32,590 --> 00:04:33,310
But...

85
00:04:36,110 --> 00:04:36,830
What is it?

86
00:04:37,470 --> 00:04:39,790
You should cut back on playing games, young man.

87
00:04:40,990 --> 00:04:41,740
Thank you for the advice.

88
00:04:41,830 --> 00:04:42,590
I'll get going.

89
00:04:48,630 --> 00:04:50,270
Double kill.

90
00:04:51,110 --> 00:04:53,150
Triple kill.

91
00:04:55,150 --> 00:04:55,910
Prof. Chen.

92
00:04:56,910 --> 00:04:57,430
What's wrong?

93
00:04:57,550 --> 00:04:58,230
I think

94
00:04:58,510 --> 00:04:59,070
this is

95
00:04:59,070 --> 00:05:00,270
a rare chance.

96
00:05:00,630 --> 00:05:01,540
What chance are you talking about?

97
00:05:02,230 --> 00:05:03,350
I mean the girl who was transported here

98
00:05:03,430 --> 00:05:04,620
from ten years ago.

99
00:05:04,750 --> 00:05:05,910
If we can conduct research on her,

100
00:05:06,470 --> 00:05:08,110
it will be a huge improvement

101
00:05:08,230 --> 00:05:09,230
in the history of mankind.

102
00:05:10,910 --> 00:05:12,430
If I hear you right,

103
00:05:13,230 --> 00:05:14,630
you plan to conduct an experiment on human.

104
00:05:15,110 --> 00:05:16,350
Do you know what does that mean?

105
00:05:16,620 --> 00:05:17,310
But Prof. Chen,

106
00:05:17,630 --> 00:05:18,990
if we miss out this chance,

107
00:05:19,430 --> 00:05:20,710
where do we find another specimen

108
00:05:20,910 --> 00:05:22,310
that had experienced time travel?

109
00:05:22,590 --> 00:05:23,510
She is not a specimen.

110
00:05:23,990 --> 00:05:24,750
She is a human.

111
00:05:25,190 --> 00:05:26,270
She is a living creature,

112
00:05:26,270 --> 00:05:27,310
just like you and me.

113
00:05:27,590 --> 00:05:29,070
But she doesn't belong to this world.

114
00:05:29,820 --> 00:05:31,140
Prof. Chen, think about it.

115
00:05:31,710 --> 00:05:32,870
If you manage to

116
00:05:33,070 --> 00:05:33,780
attain the slightest breakthrough

117
00:05:33,780 --> 00:05:34,909
through her,

118
00:05:34,909 --> 00:05:36,270
you will become

119
00:05:36,270 --> 00:05:37,470
the greatest scientist in the world.

120
00:05:37,470 --> 00:05:38,270
I'm sorry.

121
00:05:39,060 --> 00:05:39,870
I don't want to be

122
00:05:39,870 --> 00:05:40,820
the greatest scientist.

123
00:05:40,820 --> 00:05:41,510
Listen.

124
00:05:41,790 --> 00:05:42,430
Science

125
00:05:42,430 --> 00:05:43,750
is meant to bring happiness to mankind.

126
00:05:43,900 --> 00:05:44,990
It's not supposed to bring threats.

127
00:05:46,950 --> 00:05:47,860
From now on,

128
00:05:48,300 --> 00:05:49,390
forget about it.

129
00:05:50,830 --> 00:05:51,710
Don't spread it.

130
00:06:09,030 --> 00:06:09,670
Darling.

131
00:06:11,790 --> 00:06:14,030
Darling, I need to go somewhere far.

132
00:06:15,390 --> 00:06:16,270
Where are you going?

133
00:06:17,190 --> 00:06:18,550
It's not about me.

134
00:06:18,990 --> 00:06:20,860
We are going there together.

135
00:06:21,510 --> 00:06:22,150
Take a look.

136
00:06:24,510 --> 00:06:25,870
What is this?

137
00:06:27,990 --> 00:06:29,070
It's from the young man who saved you,

138
00:06:29,070 --> 00:06:30,150
[Notification on Recuperation Programme]
Xiao Dong.

139
00:06:30,590 --> 00:06:31,550
[Notification on Recuperation Programme]
I contacted him

140
00:06:31,550 --> 00:06:32,630
[Notification on Recuperation Programme]
to pay him back

141
00:06:32,630 --> 00:06:33,310
the hospital bill.

142
00:06:33,870 --> 00:06:35,550
He heard about your health condition.

143
00:06:35,790 --> 00:06:36,790
He said he knew of

144
00:06:36,790 --> 00:06:37,950
a nursing home

145
00:06:38,140 --> 00:06:39,350
in the city

146
00:06:39,510 --> 00:06:41,190
which is having a charity campaign.

147
00:06:41,710 --> 00:06:42,790
All the expenses

148
00:06:43,420 --> 00:06:45,230
is covered by a game designer, Winter

149
00:06:45,230 --> 00:06:46,500
with public welfare fund.

150
00:06:46,830 --> 00:06:48,110
So, he applied it for us.

151
00:06:48,230 --> 00:06:49,070
Surprisingly,

152
00:06:49,950 --> 00:06:51,230
the application is allowed.

153
00:06:51,590 --> 00:06:53,150
So, he sent us the letter.

154
00:06:54,790 --> 00:06:55,550
Darling,

155
00:06:55,950 --> 00:06:56,670
this time,

156
00:06:56,990 --> 00:06:57,940
you can join the nursing home

157
00:06:57,940 --> 00:06:58,750
for recuperation.

158
00:06:59,670 --> 00:07:00,910
I don't need it.

159
00:07:01,510 --> 00:07:02,750
You need it badly.

160
00:07:02,780 --> 00:07:03,790
In order to find our daughter,

161
00:07:03,990 --> 00:07:05,270
you started to have hallucination.

162
00:07:05,420 --> 00:07:06,870
No, that's not hallucination.

163
00:07:06,870 --> 00:07:08,150
I really heard her!

164
00:07:08,150 --> 00:07:09,470
Furthermore, I saw her with my own eyes.

165
00:07:09,910 --> 00:07:11,470
Yes, I got it.

166
00:07:12,190 --> 00:07:13,830
Since they offered to help us,

167
00:07:14,110 --> 00:07:15,100
we should not turn down

168
00:07:15,100 --> 00:07:16,470
their kindness.

169
00:07:17,430 --> 00:07:19,150
You must take good care of yourself

170
00:07:19,230 --> 00:07:20,550
so that we have enough energy

171
00:07:20,590 --> 00:07:21,510
to look for our daughter.

172
00:07:22,510 --> 00:07:23,190
Am I right?

173
00:07:24,030 --> 00:07:25,430
You are right.

174
00:07:27,909 --> 00:07:29,270
I have to take good care of myself

175
00:07:29,909 --> 00:07:30,670
so that I can

176
00:07:30,670 --> 00:07:31,630
wait for my daughter to come home.

177
00:07:31,950 --> 00:07:32,550
Yes.

178
00:07:32,750 --> 00:07:33,230
That's a deal.

179
00:07:33,230 --> 00:07:33,830
Let's pack up.

180
00:07:33,830 --> 00:07:34,900
Let's go.

181
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:45,430
[Winter: I'll send your parents to nursing home with "Battle of the Saints" kind fund]

182
00:07:45,430 --> 00:07:46,800
[It's free. I wish your mom a speedy recovery.]

183
00:07:47,220 --> 00:07:48,790
Xu Xiao Dong.

184
00:07:48,830 --> 00:07:49,630
What's wrong?

185
00:07:52,550 --> 00:07:53,510
Winter's foundation

186
00:07:53,510 --> 00:07:54,150
made arrangement to send my parents

187
00:07:54,150 --> 00:07:54,990
to a nursing home.

188
00:07:57,190 --> 00:07:58,150
How did he know that?

189
00:08:00,190 --> 00:08:01,390
Two days ago, I left him a comment

190
00:08:01,390 --> 00:08:03,070
telling him I found my name.

191
00:08:03,950 --> 00:08:04,590
Of course,

192
00:08:04,590 --> 00:08:05,750
I did tell him that

193
00:08:05,750 --> 00:08:06,630
due to an accident,

194
00:08:06,630 --> 00:08:07,550
I can't take care of my parents.

195
00:08:08,230 --> 00:08:09,470
However, I really didn't expect that

196
00:08:09,470 --> 00:08:10,270
he would help me out.

197
00:08:10,950 --> 00:08:12,190
It's so touching.

198
00:08:13,230 --> 00:08:14,620
As your dream man,

199
00:08:14,790 --> 00:08:15,910
I think he can be considered

200
00:08:16,190 --> 00:08:17,590
to have passed the threshold.

201
00:08:18,990 --> 00:08:20,030
How could you say that?

202
00:08:20,190 --> 00:08:21,630
He is perfect!

203
00:08:24,830 --> 00:08:26,030
I didn't expect that

204
00:08:26,030 --> 00:08:26,750
I would meet

205
00:08:26,750 --> 00:08:27,380
my first friend

206
00:08:27,380 --> 00:08:28,700
on the internet.

207
00:08:28,830 --> 00:08:29,990
He is also a super cool guy.

208
00:08:33,100 --> 00:08:33,980
Isn't me

209
00:08:33,980 --> 00:08:34,990
your first friend?

210
00:08:36,030 --> 00:08:37,590
You are the first bad guy I met.

211
00:08:40,110 --> 00:08:40,750
Of course,

212
00:08:40,750 --> 00:08:42,110
you are nice to me now.

213
00:08:50,550 --> 00:08:51,270
Have my parents

214
00:08:51,270 --> 00:08:52,230
gone to the nursing home?

215
00:08:53,510 --> 00:08:54,270
Let's check on them.

216
00:08:56,350 --> 00:08:57,070
I mean let's go my home.

217
00:08:58,470 --> 00:08:59,470
Let's go.

218
00:08:59,710 --> 00:09:00,510
Why are you in a rush?

219
00:09:06,950 --> 00:09:07,910
What does that mean?

220
00:09:08,710 --> 00:09:09,950
It has been a long time

221
00:09:10,310 --> 00:09:11,430
and you haven't found her?

222
00:09:13,110 --> 00:09:13,870
Yes, Director Wei.

223
00:09:14,310 --> 00:09:15,670
Due to the venue,

224
00:09:15,670 --> 00:09:16,310
none of the security cameras

225
00:09:16,310 --> 00:09:17,350
had taken any photo.

226
00:09:18,030 --> 00:09:18,710
Furthermore,

227
00:09:18,710 --> 00:09:19,830
Mr. and Mrs. Lei are not home lately.

228
00:09:22,030 --> 00:09:23,430
No, keep looking.

229
00:09:23,550 --> 00:09:24,670
Make sure you find her.

230
00:09:24,670 --> 00:09:25,310
Okay, Director Wei.

231
00:09:26,270 --> 00:09:27,030
Xuan He.

232
00:09:27,590 --> 00:09:28,510
Don't panic.

233
00:09:28,910 --> 00:09:29,630
Take a seat.

234
00:09:32,150 --> 00:09:33,990
You are exhausted.

235
00:09:33,990 --> 00:09:35,190
Perhaps you saw it wrongly.

236
00:09:35,550 --> 00:09:36,950
She's been missing in action for ten years.

237
00:09:37,990 --> 00:09:39,750
She wouldn't have had appeared out of no where.

238
00:09:39,830 --> 00:09:41,110
No way I saw it wrongly.

239
00:09:41,510 --> 00:09:42,300
She was there.

240
00:09:44,670 --> 00:09:46,550
All right, stop thinking too much.

241
00:09:46,830 --> 00:09:48,950
Today, I baked some biscuits.

242
00:09:49,030 --> 00:09:49,590
Try it.

243
00:09:51,470 --> 00:09:52,350
It's fresh from the oven.

244
00:09:59,390 --> 00:10:00,110
[Chu Xia.]

245
00:10:02,070 --> 00:10:02,830
No.

246
00:10:03,710 --> 00:10:04,740
I must find her.

247
00:10:05,310 --> 00:10:06,350
You should go back first.

248
00:10:06,590 --> 00:10:07,590
I have something else to do.

249
00:10:21,710 --> 00:10:22,390
Xuan He.

250
00:10:23,430 --> 00:10:25,030
As expected, once Lei Chu Xia appears,

251
00:10:25,670 --> 00:10:27,110
you start to neglect me.

252
00:10:39,500 --> 00:10:40,190
Director Zhao.

253
00:10:40,510 --> 00:10:41,670
I'm sorry, Director Wei.

254
00:10:42,190 --> 00:10:43,710
Director Zhao insists to see you.

255
00:10:45,230 --> 00:10:45,950
Director Wei,

256
00:10:45,950 --> 00:10:47,100
why are you troubled?

257
00:10:47,470 --> 00:10:48,070
Nothing.

258
00:10:49,110 --> 00:10:50,070
Are you thinking about

259
00:10:50,070 --> 00:10:51,470
the intelligent system

260
00:10:51,470 --> 00:10:52,110
that will be launched soon,

261
00:10:52,110 --> 00:10:53,260
the Family First app?

262
00:10:55,670 --> 00:10:56,470
I heard about it.

263
00:10:57,070 --> 00:10:57,790
For this app,

264
00:10:57,790 --> 00:10:58,670
there are some technical issues

265
00:10:58,670 --> 00:10:59,470
which haven't been resolved.

266
00:11:00,150 --> 00:11:01,510
That's why it took a long time to launch.

267
00:11:02,060 --> 00:11:02,990
As one of the investors

268
00:11:02,990 --> 00:11:03,870
of this project,

269
00:11:04,590 --> 00:11:05,580
I'm quite worried.

270
00:11:08,590 --> 00:11:09,750
Director, don't worry.

271
00:11:10,470 --> 00:11:11,870
I'm the founder of Cyber Tech.

272
00:11:12,070 --> 00:11:13,310
I care about

273
00:11:13,710 --> 00:11:15,230
the Family First app more than anyone else.

274
00:11:15,910 --> 00:11:16,870
Our R&D team

275
00:11:16,870 --> 00:11:17,900
is full of talented people.

276
00:11:17,900 --> 00:11:18,910
We will surely have a breakthrough

277
00:11:19,110 --> 00:11:20,190
on the technical issues.

278
00:11:21,750 --> 00:11:23,150
I'm not as optimistic as you, Director Wei.

279
00:11:23,670 --> 00:11:25,790
Speed is the soul of the internet.

280
00:11:28,550 --> 00:11:30,150
This is the information of the companies

281
00:11:30,150 --> 00:11:32,070
which are also working on an app similar to Family First.

282
00:11:33,070 --> 00:11:35,470
They are a bunch of talented people

283
00:11:35,750 --> 00:11:37,630
without support and background.

284
00:11:37,920 --> 00:11:38,800
[Company information]

285
00:11:40,510 --> 00:11:42,510
Director Wei, I have a proposal.

286
00:11:42,950 --> 00:11:44,630
Why don't we change our mindset?

287
00:11:45,390 --> 00:11:47,190
Since your team is unable to solve the issues,

288
00:11:47,750 --> 00:11:48,630
why don't we

289
00:11:48,700 --> 00:11:49,510
draw on the experience

290
00:11:49,510 --> 00:11:50,270
of others?

291
00:11:53,870 --> 00:11:55,350
This is plagiarism.

292
00:11:59,990 --> 00:12:00,710
Director Wei.

293
00:12:01,670 --> 00:12:03,350
Didn't we do the same

294
00:12:04,590 --> 00:12:05,710
ten years ago?

